Detailed Description

Struct to hold info about the file format for variable.

Description:

Holds information pertinent to file IO for a variable.

NOTE: purposefully do not have any dynamically allocated bits in here or we have to have a special free call (see _FC_DsFileIOInfo).

Modifications:

  • 7/18/2005 WSD created.
